{"tid":1740582,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"政府份聲明稿，得「高度自治」係無括號","createTime":"2019-11-20T03:45:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T03:47:15.000Z","uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f9d88339012779e693922bbd9e5f00c519cebc66","tid":1740582,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:45:38.000Z","msg":"「自回歸以來，香港特別行政區一直嚴格按照《中華人民共和國香港特別行政區基本法》的規定實行『港人治港』、<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">高度自治</span></span>，充分體現『一國兩制』得到全面和成功落實。『一國兩制』是保持香港長期繁榮穩定、市民安居樂業的最佳安排，特區政府會繼續堅定不移地按照《基本法》落實『一國兩制』方針。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b80c3a74874cf749aba38f14fd47fdd9059928e","tid":1740582,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:47:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201911/20/P2019112000034.htm?fontSize=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201911%2F20%2FP2019112000034.htm%3FfontSize%3D1&d=qnfk3FWFLoR313jZLhvcNm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=4ec47d70\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201911/20/P2019112000034.htm?fontSize=1</a>"}]}